snippet.title: STRIDE: Fates - Official Slums Gameplay Reveal Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Here's the latest Stride: Fates trailer, showing off some gameplay from the parkour action VR game's upcoming single-player campaign mode. From traversing the rooftops and flying with drones to sneaking up on enemies with guns and melee weapons, here's what to expect when Stride: Fates arrives in 2023.
